$p\left(x_{1}, x_{2}\right)=p_{1}\left(x_{1}\right) p_{2}\left(x_{2}\right) \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} c_{k} a_{k} L_{k}^{\alpha_{1}}\left(x_{1}\right) L_{k}^{\alpha_{2}}\left(x_{2}\right)$, где $0 \leqslant x_{v}<\infty, \alpha_{v} \geqslant \gamma>-1, \rho_{v}\left(x_{v}\right)=x_{v}^{\alpha} e^{-x} v / \Gamma\left(\alpha_{v}+1\right)$, $L_{k}^{\alpha} v\left(x_{v}\right)$ - Лагерра многочлены, ортонормированные на положительной полуоси с весом $p_{v}\left(x_{v}\right), v=1,2$;

\[
\begin{gathered}
a_{k}=\frac{\Gamma(\gamma+k+1)}{\Gamma(\gamma+1)} \sqrt{\frac{\Gamma\left(\alpha_{1}+1\right) \Gamma\left(\alpha_{2}+1\right)}{\Gamma\left(\alpha_{1}+k+1\right) \Gamma\left(\alpha_{2}+k+1\right)}}, \\
c_{k}=\int_{0}^{1} \lambda^{k} d F(\lambda), \quad k=0,1,2, \ldots,
\end{gathered}
\]

